{"tid":1777392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【力抗死亡之吻】老字號粥麵店 澄清與譚詠麟關係：100%完全無關","createTime":"2019-12-10T07:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T10:14:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28a96bd359ca613dac3785ab95a87e48286e3c93","tid":1777392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"抗暴之戰中，不少建制派或撐警名人，一旦高調撐餐廳，往往引起反效果，如葉劉淑儀撐加記、陳百祥愛去漢發麵家，被視為死亡之吻。今月初就有網民發帖，指老牌雲吞麵店正斗粥麵專家，老闆何冠明是和譚詠麟合資經營，更指網站沒有寫，並不代表譚詠麟不是老闆之一云云。<br />\n<br />\n記者以此傳聞向正斗查詢，老闆透過公關斬釘截鐵回應﹕「100%沒有關係」，公關表示，正斗是由何氏家族擁有，70多年來都是由何氏家族持有，沒有外來投資，譚詠麟亦從不是股東或有合作關係﹕「在運動發生前，如果有明星投資餐飲，餐廳一定會把明星當成宣傳。」而他們餐廳「從來沒有拿（譚詠麟）作宣傳」。<br />\n<br />\n正斗現於香港有7間分店，分別以正斗及何洪記為名。餐廳是香港老字號，1946年，現任掌舵人何冠明先翁何釗洪創立何洪記，他是雲吞麵大王麥煥池的唯一入 室弟子。對雲吞麵、乾炒牛河等港式美食極盡講究，單是雲吞麵，都以12345為口號，即一斤大地魚、兩斤蝦角、三斤豬骨、四両蝦子、五大筒水，所以出品多年來都維持水準，多年來都入選米芝蓮推介。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191209/large/1575890466_a9f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191209%2Flarge%2F1575890466_a9f2.jpg&h=37ab1223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/ETW/20191209/XBTCJM7FHW2L62CUDIRFMDXIXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20191209%2FXBTCJM7FHW2L62CUDIRFMDXIXQ%2F&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=cc52272d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20191209%2FXBTCJM7FHW2L62CUDIRFMDXIXQ%2F&h=e3bc501d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/ETW/20191209/XBTCJM7FHW2L62CUDIRFMDXIXQ/</a>"},{"pid":"33217eee7e473688255844684e0647f3e5b220b9","tid":1777392,"uid":201526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b0c47809d4f8ab8254c974c1125993fac4af93","tid":1777392,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:53:50.000Z","msg":"譚校長喎, 唔係生招牌嚟咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99830bca05e757f58f2b53baac11206f1baadd37","tid":1777392,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:55:17.000Z","msg":"旺角魚街口間臭豆腐，大大張譚詠倫合照貼喺度，咪一樣咁撚多港豬塞喺度食，仲好多中學生"},{"pid":"4ae53759b22e72dfa75b513a174ff3f547936a72","tid":1777392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33217eee7e473688255844684e0647f3e5b220b9","tid":1777392,"uid":201526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"原本上左神枱，而家直插落谷底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}